<strong>Professional Language</strong>

<em>Cross out the statements that are NOT professional.</em>
<ol>
 	<li>I am very interested in a job at ABC, Inc.</li>
 	<li>I would like this job, but first I need to know how much you will pay me.</li>
 	<li>I ain’t got no typin’ skills.</li>
 	<li>I have three years of experience using Microsoft Excel.</li>
 	<li>My customer service skills used to be pretty crappy, but I have been practicing and am now comfortable interacting with customers.</li>
</ol>
<em>Write your own professional and unprofessional cover letter sentences! See if a partner can guess which are the unprofessional ones!</em>
